How does it feel when you are able to express your emotions using emojis when chattting with your friends?

How would you feel if you are able to create emojis yourself?

In this project you  will learn how write a program to show  how you feel on your micro:bit.


Programming Language 

     Microsoft Makecode Python

Coding environment / Text editor

     https://makecode.microbit.org/#editor


Parts of the micro:bit

       The part of the micro:bit used in this projet is the LEDs(Light Emitting Diode). It shows or displays how we feel.


Programming concepts

       Function: A function is a reusable block of code that performs a specific task or a set of tasks.

       In the program below, a forever function makes your emoji loop or repeat over and over again


Code / Program

def on_forever():
    basic.show_leds("""
        . # . # .
        . . . . .
        # . . . #
        . # # # .
        . . . . .
        """)
basic.forever(on_forever)



